OL,7,BThe INternet f 14 and 15-W  o{{{{{{uj} 
OL,8,Bclaim to have playedEscratchcardsBin   
OL,9,Bthe last year, claims a new study.     
OL,11,BExeter University surveyed 22,067 young
OL,12,Bpeople aged 12-15 and found that 45% of
OL,13,Bolder boys and 40% of older girls had  
OL,14,Bplayed scratchcards in the last year.  
OL,16,BScratchcardsBare proving too much for  
OL,17,Bsome teenagers to resist.EClub 140B    
OL,18,Bfinds out why gambling has gripped us. 
