OL,7,BCamelot say its own independent surveys
OL,8,Bshow teenageEgambling isEon the decline
OL,10,B"Our last study showed 15% of teens    
OL,11,Bwere playing scratchcards but only 6%  
OL,12,Bwere actuallyEbuying themBin person,"  
OL,13,Bsays Camelot spokeswoman Louise Harvey.
OL,15,B"Whatever theBactual figures are, any  
OL,16,Eunderage gamblingBhas to be stamped out
OL,17,Band weBcommit ourselves to raising     
OL,18,Bawareness about it," she adds.         
