OL,6,                          V ///////   
OL,7,BThe most addictive activity is the type
OL,8,Bwhere theEresult is known quickly,Bsays
OL,9,BPatrick, a former gambler and spokesman
OL,10,BforEGamblers Anonymous.                
OL,12,B"Scratchcards areEheart-stoppers.BYou  
OL,13,Bscratch off two squares to reveal two  
OL,14,B#50,000 figures, and hope a third one  
OL,15,Bwill match.BIt's allEover in 2 seconds.
OL,17,B"Some younger people don't realise they
OL,18,Bhave a gambling problem. Some are even 
OL,19,Eencouraged by their parents,"Bhe adds. 
