OL,7,BNational Lottery organisersECamelotBsay
OL,8,Bthey're trying to stamp out the sale of
OL,9,Bscratchcards to young people under 16. 
OL,11,B"We'reEcracking down on the retailers,"
OL,12,Bsays Camelot's Louise Harvey. "Together
OL,13,Bwith the Trading Standards Authority,  
OL,14,Bwe're sending kids to test whether     
OL,15,Bshopkeepers are selling tickets to     
OL,16,Bunderage people."                      
OL,18,B"You can report a retailer who is      
OL,19,Bselling to under 16s on our hotline."  
