OL,7,BHere's what Teletext'sENew Centurions  
OL,8,Bthink about teenage gambling.          
OL,10,E Katie-Anne Best, 15:B"When I did work
OL,11,Bexperience at a local radio station,   
OL,12,Bthey sent me out to newsagents as a    
OL,13,Btest. All of them sold me Lottery      
OL,14,Btickets even though I was only 14."    
OL,16,EELuke Ribbons, 15:B"I've bought one or
OL,17,Btwo. I won #1 once but haven't bothered
OL,18,Bcashing it in yet. I wouldn't go crazy 
OL,19,Band buy loads of tickets though."      
